'''2007年安托法加斯塔地震'''是于2007年11月14日15:40:53 [[UTC|UTC]]（当地时间12:40:53）在[[智利|智利]]发生的一次[[地震|地震]]。震中位于[[托科皮亚|托科皮亚]]以东35公里处，地震影响到[[智利|智利]]东北部[[塔拉帕卡大区|塔拉帕卡大区]]與[[安托法加斯塔大区|安托法加斯塔大区]]。地震强度达到里氏7.7级，<ref name="usgs"/><ref name="usgs_en">[http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2007jsat.php Magnitude 7.7 Antofagasta, Chile] {{Wayback|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2007jsat.php |date=20071116161427 }} by [[美国地质调查局|USGS]]，in English</ref>持续大约50秒。<ref>Terra.cl, 14/11/07, ''[http://www.terra.cl/noticias/index.cfm?id_reg=878501&id_cat=302 «Fuerte sismo sacudió esta tarde al Norte del País»] {{Wayback|url=http://www.terra.cl/noticias/index.cfm?id_reg=878501&id_cat=302 |date=20080120071042 }}''</ref>之后发生了8次超过里氏5.0级的[[余震|余震]]，其中有两次达到6.8及6.2级。<ref>[http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2007jtaz.php Magnitude 6.8, Antofagasta earthquake] {{Wayback|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2007jtaz.php |date=20071116233152 }} of 15 November 2007</ref>[[太平洋海啸警报中心|太平洋海啸警报中心]]当即发出[[海啸|海啸]]警报，但1小时后取消警报。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/ptwc/ |title=NOAA Pacific Tsunami Warning Center |accessdate=2007-11-16 |archive-date=2019-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721032751/https://www.prh.noaa.gov/ptwc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.prh.noaa.gov/ptwc/messages/pacific/2007/pacific.2007.11.14.165356.txt Cancellation bulletin] {{Wayback|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/ptwc/messages/pacific/2007/pacific.2007.11.14.165356.txt |date=20131104173324 }} issued by the PTWC</ref>

距震中1245千米及700千米的[[圣地亚哥_(智利)|圣地亚哥]]及[[拉巴斯|拉巴斯]]均有震感。<ref name=AFP>[http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5j0lyUZAnd-WZqnex4RvEPH2GsCjA Strong earthquake shakes northern Chile, kills at least two] {{Wayback|url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5j0lyUZAnd-WZqnex4RvEPH2GsCjA |date=20071116135724 }} AFP news report</ref>

== 伤亡及损失 ==
至少两人因地震死亡，分别是一位88岁的老妇人和一名54岁的妇女<ref name=AFP/>，並至少造成150人受伤。<ref>[http://ca.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-11-14T220750Z_01_N14189438_RTRIDST_0_NEWS-QUAKE-CHILE-COL.XML Big earthquake kills two in Chile and hits mining] {{Wayback|url=http://ca.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-11-14T220750Z_01_N14189438_RTRIDST_0_NEWS-QUAKE-CHILE-COL.XML |date=20080113163317 }}，Reuters, [[Canada|Canada]]</ref><ref name=BBC/>地震同时造成了该地区大面积停电。由于该地区是世界重要[[铜|铜]]产区，国际铜价当即上扬6%，[[锡|锡]]价也上涨4%创下新高。<ref>[http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,22762597-20142,00.html Metals prices up after Chile quake] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,22762597-20142,00.html |date=20071118072941 }} The Australian Business</ref>还有报道指出，修路工人被困在坍塌的高速公路隧道中。<ref>[http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/latest/200711151101/workers_trapped_in_tunnel_collapse_after_quakes Workers trapped in tunnel collapse after quakes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/latest/200711151101/workers_trapped_in_tunnel_collapse_after_quakes |date=20120207165849 }}，Radio New Zealand News</ref>

地震造成4000所住房倒塌，15000人被迫转移。单[[托科皮亚|托科皮亚]]一市就有1200所住房毁坏，全市30%的建筑损毁。<ref name=BBC/>

